Method Detail

findAU

public static final AUComponent findAU(ComponentDescription desc)
Determine the next AUComponent as specified. Will return null if it cannot find a component that matches the specifications. The type of the ComponentDescription is set to AUConstants.kAudioUnitComponentType iff all of the type, subtype and manu fields are not specified. Thus - in that case, it will find audio units of a v1 'aunt' type. If the type is specified, no adjustment is made to the component description.

findNextAU

public final AUComponent findNextAU(ComponentDescription desc)
Determine the next Component as specified. Will return null if it cannot find a component that matches the specifications. The type of the ComponentDescription is set to AUConstants.kAudioUnitComponentType

openAU

public AudioUnit openAU()
Given a component identifier it opens the specified component.

Recommend using the open() call as it can throw an exception if there is an error encountered when the component is opened.
